goals__remit: Dalmatian is involved in the air and sea transport sector and is in the process of establishing several subsidiary LCC airline companies within the EU and future joint venture partnerships in Australia, Asia and North America. The aim of the company is to create a global brand and a quality service based on high safety standards. The goup is also in the process of establishing a sea ferry service subsidiary within the EU for transport of passenger and road transport vehicles.
